1929;;Honky Tonk;;American;;Lloyd Bacon;;Sophie Tucker, Lila Lee;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honky_Tonk_(1929_film);;Sophie Tucker plays Sophie Leonard, a singer in a nightclub who at great sacrifice sends her daughter Beth (Lila Lee) to Europe to be educated, keeping her work as an entertainer a secret from her. When the grown-up, expensively educated Beth returns to America, she is shocked to discover her mother's true profession and disowns her, breaking Sophie's heart.